39585/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Recognition+and+management+of+intra-abdominal+hypertension+and+abdominal+compartment+syndrome&amp;author=R+Nagappan&amp;author=D+Ernest&amp;author=A+Whitfield&amp;publication_year=2005&amp;journal=Crit+Care+Resusc&amp;pages=298-302&amp;pmid=16539585">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">63.</div><div id="r63" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Pickhardt PJ, Shimony JS, Heiken JP, Buchman TG, Fisher AJ. The abdominal compartment syndrome: CT findings. <em>AJR Am J Roentgenol</em> 1999;173(3):575–579.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.2214/ajr.173.3.10470882">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10470882/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=The+abdominal+compartment+syndrome%3A+CT+findings&amp;author=PJ+Pickhardt&amp;author=JS+Shimony&amp;author=JP+Heiken&amp;author=TG+Buchman&amp;author=AJ+Fisher&amp;publication_year=1999&amp;journal=AJR+Am+J+Roentgenol&amp;pages=575-579&amp;doi=10.2214%2Fajr.173.3.10470882&amp;pmid=10470882">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">64.</div><div id="r64" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Al-Bahrani AZ, Abid GH, Sahgal E, O’Shea S, Lee S, Ammori BJ. A prospective evaluation of CT features predictive of intra-abdominal hypertension and abdominal compartment syndrome in critically ill surgical patients. <em>Clin Radiol</em> 2007;62(7):676–682.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.crad.2006.11.006">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.